title: S16 Ep126: Supernatural Stories Live with guest Nikki Folsom
itunes:title: Supernatural Stories Live with guest Nikki Folsom
description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural Stories Live with guest Nikki Folsom

Darkness Dave set sail aboard the Jericho Cruise through the Bermuda Triangle and hosted a Live Podcast with guest Nikki Folsom. Dave & Nikki discuss Fairies, Cryptids, Shadow People and Ghosts with Live Audience participation sharing Supernatural Stories.

Sign up now for The Jericho Cruise in March 2022: https://www.chrisjerichocruise.com/
